com.qti.snapdragon.sdk.digitalpen

Interface DigitalPenManager.PowerStateChangedListener

  • Enclosing class:
    DigitalPenManager

    public static interface DigitalPenManager.PowerStateChangedListener
    The listener interface for receiving Power State Changed events, which indicate the framework has changed power state. Clients interested in this information should add a listener with DigitalPenManager.setPowerStateChangedListener(PowerStateChangedListener)
